reviewText: what a turd of a wannabe arthouse "film".....no plot to speak of ...the only remotely interesting parts are the softcore bondage porn flash cut nonsense between the so-called scenes....and after the 500th time they get reused to fluff the run time even that gets old  despite the scorching hot  red head....mind of a sociopath indeed ...if he were on  an od of Prozac at Disneyworld ....laaaaame!

ugh  terrible.  should have known when the grammatical errors appeared in the intro text.

this video, im guessing, was a college film course final project.
